metadata.title: EPIC - Enhancement Planning and Information Control system (Canada)

creators.name: Oceans Canada, Science Branch - Data Analyst

metadata.description:
Parameter
Biological data sampled from adult and jack hatchery reared salmonids

Measurement Details
"Data include planned and actual egg targets, eggs taken, juveniles released, and 
adults recovered, biostandards for egg-to-release and release-to-return survivals, age distributions and catch distributions."

[ A TCODE project ]
